&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Use Kafka, Redis, Cassandra, Elasticsearch and other open-source components&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
