&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Be the technical owner of multiple critical systems or architecture areas, often spanning several teams or product lines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Drive the design and delivery of high-scale, high-impact projects, from vision to execution in production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Build consensus and alignment across stakeholders on key architectural decisions and long-term strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Deeply investigate and optimize performance, reliability, and efficiency in large-scale distributed systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Collaborate with Staff Engineers, Directors, and VPs across the company to shape Datadog’s technical roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-prosemirror-content-type=&quot;node&quot; data-prosemirror-node-name=&quot;paragraph&quot; data-prosemirror-node-block=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Guide teams through ambiguity, scaling challenges, and evolving requirements with clear technical direction.&lt;/li&gt;
